## 🛠️ Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|---|---|
| Frontend | React 18, HTML5, CSS3 (custom vars), Babel (browser) |
| Backend | Node.js, Express.js |
| Database | MongoDB + Mongoose ODM |
| Real-time | Socket.io (WebSockets) |
| Auth | JWT + bcryptjs |
| Fonts | Orbitron, Syne, Space Grotesk |

---

## 🎨 Design Highlights

- **Dark theme** with colorful accent system (violet, cyan, pink, green, orange)
- **Orbitron** font for scores/timers → futuristic feel
- **Syne** for headings → bold & modern
- CSS custom properties for instant theming
- Smooth animations: fadeUp, float, pulse, slideIn
- Gradient borders on stat cards
- Live pulse dot for active rooms
- Real-time thinking indicators for opponents

